{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it mandatory that all disabled toilets should be fitted with a bidet",
        "additional_details": "For all businesses/buildings where it is mandatory to provide an accessible toilet it should also be mandatory to provide a bidet within those toilets. This would including pubs, restaurants, leisure facilities, and travel accommodations.\r\n \r\nWe believe would help those individuals that require this service to live a more independent life and not miss out on the things other people participate in without barriers.\r\n",
        "background": "We would like you to make it mandatory that all disabled toilets are fitted with a bidet (wash & dry toilets). ",
